rt-club-music/38252769/|title=\u2018Real Housewives\u2019 star Erika Jayne lives out loud|work=Detroit News|access-date=2018-10-24|language=en}}</ref> She hosted the [[Billboard Music Award|''Billboard Music Awards Red Carpet Live'']] alongside AJ Gibson on May 20, 2018.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/bbma/8456667/billboard-music-awards-2018-red-carpet-pre-show|title=Billboard Music Awards 2018: Hosts Announced For Official Red Carpet Pre-Show|work=Billboard|access-date=2018-05-25}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-5751293/Billboards-2018-Erika-Jayne-puts-legs-display-mini.html|title=Billboards 2018: Erika Jayne puts her legs on display in a mini|work=Mail Online|access-date=2018-05-25}}</ref> The following August, she announced her collaboration with [[ShoeDazzle]], an online shoe and accessories website.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BmMTfPyA3iq/|title=Erika Jayne on Instagram: \"Coming soon... \ud83d\udc60\"|website=Instagram|language=en|access-date=2018-08-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bravotv.com/the-real-housewives-of-beverly-hills/lookbook/erika-girardi-teased-shoe-collaboration-with-shoedazzle|title=Erika Girardi Just Teased a New Fashion Collab and We\u2019re Freaking Out|last=|first=|date=2018-08-08|work=Bravo TV Official Site|access-date=2018-08-09|language=en-US}}</ref> ShoeDazzle's commercial campaign features Jayne and her single \"[[Xxpensive|Xxpen$ive]]\".<ref name=\":9\">{{Cite news|url=https://people.com/style/erika-girardi-shoedazzle-commercial/|title=Get RHOBH Star Erika Girardi's Signature Style Thanks to Her New Partnership with ShoeDazzle|work=PEOPLE.com|access-date=2018-09-04|language=en}}</ref> She teamed up with ShoeDazzle as their latest \u201c[[Muses|muse]]\u201d and shared her 14 must-have favorite shoe styles for fall 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.shoedazzle.com/index.cfm?action=catalog.shop_influencer&influencer=erika_jayne&bp=0&code